query: WITH entities AS (SELECT customer_id, created_at, id FROM deposits WHERE (customer_id = $1) AND (((created_at, id) > ($4, $3)) OR $3 IS NULL) ORDER BY created_at, id LIMIT $2) SELECT i.id AS "entity_id: DepositId", e.sequence, e.event, e.recorded_at FROM entities i JOIN deposit_events e ON i.id = e.id ORDER BY i.created_at, i.id, i.id, e.sequence
